Preferences can be configured in one of two ways:

- By specifying:
  - `doNotDisturb` (boolean)
  - `outOfOffice` (boolean)
- Or, by specifying:
  - `doNotDisturb` (boolean)
  - `outOfOffice` (boolean | string)
  - `useSystemTheme` (boolean)
  - `theme` (string)

1. [ ] Run the code as-is to see the error.
2. [ ] Fix the compile-time bug by updating the incorrect overload signature to use the types listed above.

